  <entry>
    <title>微分方程模型-人口模型</title>
    <link href="http://yoursite.com/wiki/%E5%BE%AE%E5%88%86%E6%96%B9%E7%A8%8B%E6%A8%A1%E5%9E%8B-%E4%BA%BA%E5%8F%A3%E6%A8%A1%E5%9E%8B/"/>
    <id>http://yoursite.com/wiki/%E5%BE%AE%E5%88%86%E6%96%B9%E7%A8%8B%E6%A8%A1%E5%9E%8B-%E4%BA%BA%E5%8F%A3%E6%A8%A1%E5%9E%8B/</id>
    <published>2020-07-06T14:21:12.000Z</published>
    <updated>2020-07-07T01:29:20.890Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<link rel="stylesheet" class="aplayer-secondary-style-marker" href="\assets\css\APlayer.min.css"><script src="\assets\js\APlayer.min.js" class="aplayer-secondary-script-marker"></script><p>人口模型主要关注人口数量随着时间如何由增长率决定，根据增长率的不同模型可以分为马尔萨斯（Malthus）模型和阻滞增长模型（Logistic 模型），另一个问题是如何利用已有的人口历史数据预测未来的人口，这涉及到参数估计问题。<br><a id="more"></a></p><h2 id="马尔萨斯（Malthus）模型"><a href="#马尔萨斯（Malthus）模型" class="headerlink" title="马尔萨斯（Malthus）模型"></a>马尔萨斯（Malthus）模型</h2><h3 id="模型假设"><a href="#模型假设" class="headerlink" title="模型假设"></a>模型假设</h3><ol><li>$x(t)$：$t$ 年的人口数，连续可微</li><li>$r$：人口增长率，为常数</li><li>不存在迁入迁出，每个个体相同<h3 id="建模分析"><a href="#建模分析" class="headerlink" title="建模分析"></a>建模分析</h3>由假设，人口增量：<script type="math/tex; mode=display">x(t+\Delta t)-x(t) = rx(t)\Delta t</script>得：<script type="math/tex; mode=display">\begin{cases}\dfrac{dx}{dt}=rx \\x(0) = x_0\end{cases}</script>解得：<script type="math/tex; mode=display">x(t) = x_0e^{rt}</script>通过MATLAB绘图如下：($x_0=10,r=0.1,t\in[0,100]$)</li></ol><p><img src="/wiki/%E5%BE%AE%E5%88%86%E6%96%B9%E7%A8%8B%E6%A8%A1%E5%9E%8B-%E4%BA%BA%E5%8F%A3%E6%A8%A1%E5%9E%8B/pic1.jpg" alt="Malthus模型"></p><p>$r&gt;0$ 时长期来看$x(t)$趋于无穷，不符合实际情况</p><h2 id="阻滞增长模型（Logistic-模型）"><a href="#阻滞增长模型（Logistic-模型）" class="headerlink" title="阻滞增长模型（Logistic 模型）"></a>阻滞增长模型（Logistic 模型）</h2><h3 id="模型假设-1"><a href="#模型假设-1" class="headerlink" title="模型假设"></a>模型假设</h3><ol><li>$r=r(x)$，且为线性减函数，即$r(x)=r_0-sx$</li><li>自然条件限制$\max x(t)=x_m$，此时$r(x_m)=0$<h3 id="建模分析-1"><a href="#建模分析-1" class="headerlink" title="建模分析"></a>建模分析</h3><script type="math/tex; mode=display">\begin{cases}\dfrac{dx}{dt}=r_0(1-\dfrac{x}{x_m})x \\x(0) = x_0\end{cases}</script>分离变量解得：<script type="math/tex; mode=display">x(t) =\frac{x_m}{1+(\dfrac{x_m}{x_0}-1)e^{-rt}}</script>分析可得以下规律：</li><li>$\lim\limits_{x \to \infty}x(t) = x_m$，即无论初始人口数量为多少，最终达到平衡</li><li>x(t)单调递增，$x=\dfrac{x_m}{2}$为拐点，此时人口增长速率最大，通过MATLAB绘图如下：($x_m=100,x_0=10,r=0.1,t\in[0,100]$)</li></ol><p><img src="/wiki/%E5%BE%AE%E5%88%86%E6%96%B9%E7%A8%8B%E6%A8%A1%E5%9E%8B-%E4%BA%BA%E5%8F%A3%E6%A8%A1%E5%9E%8B/pic2.jpg" alt="Logistic模型"></p><h2 id="人口预报"><a href="#人口预报" class="headerlink" title="人口预报"></a>人口预报</h2><h3 id="建模与求解"><a href="#建模与求解" class="headerlink" title="建模与求解"></a>建模与求解</h3><p>数据是1790-2000年美国人口的统计数据（单位：百万人），建立Logistic模型：</p><script type="math/tex; mode=display">\begin{cases}\dfrac{dx}{dt}=r_0(1-\dfrac{x}{x_m})x \\x(t_0) = x_0\end{cases}</script><script type="math/tex; mode=display">\Rightarrow x(t) =\frac{x_m}{1+(\dfrac{x_m}{x_0}-1)e^{-r(t-t_0)}}</script><h3 id="参数估计"><a href="#参数估计" class="headerlink" title="参数估计"></a>参数估计</h3><h4 id="非线性最小二乘估计"><a href="#非线性最小二乘估计" class="headerlink" title="非线性最小二乘估计"></a>非线性最小二乘估计</h4><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">clc, clear</span><br><span class="line">a&#x3D;textread(&#39;data4.txt&#39;); %把原始数据保存在纯文本文件data4.txt中</span><br><span class="line">x&#x3D;a([2:2:6],:)&#39;;   %提出人口数据</span><br><span class="line">x&#x3D;nonzeros(x);  %去掉后面的零，并变成列向量</span><br><span class="line">t&#x3D;[1790:10:2000]&#39;;</span><br><span class="line">t0&#x3D;t(1); x0&#x3D;x(1);</span><br><span class="line">fun&#x3D;@(cs,td)cs(1).&#x2F;(1+(cs(1)&#x2F;x0-1)*exp(-cs(2)*(td-t0))); %cs(1)&#x3D;xm,cs(2)&#x3D;r</span><br><span class="line">cs&#x3D;lsqcurvefit(fun,rand(2,1),t(2:end),x(2:end),zeros(2,1))</span><br><span class="line">xhat&#x3D;fun(cs,[t;2010])  %预测已知年代和2010年的人口</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>最后得到：$x_m=342.4382,r=0.0274,2010$年预测人口数为$282.6784$百万人</p><h4 id="线性最小二乘法"><a href="#线性最小二乘法" class="headerlink" title="线性最小二乘法"></a>线性最小二乘法</h4><p>向后差分：<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">clc, clear</span><br><span class="line">a&#x3D;textread(&#39;data4.txt&#39;); %把原始数据保存在纯文本文件data4.txt中</span><br><span class="line">x&#x3D;a([2:2:6],:)&#39;; x&#x3D;nonzeros(x);</span><br><span class="line">t&#x3D;[1790:10:2000]&#39;;</span><br><span class="line">a&#x3D;[ones(21,1), -x(2:end)]; </span><br><span class="line">b&#x3D;diff(x).&#x2F;x(2:end)&#x2F;10;</span><br><span class="line">cs&#x3D;a\b;</span><br><span class="line">r&#x3D;cs(1), xm&#x3D;r&#x2F;cs(2)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><br>求得：$x_m=373.5135,r=0.0247$<br>向前差分：<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">clc, clear</span><br><span class="line">a&#x3D;textread(&#39;data4.txt&#39;); %把原始数据保存在纯文本文件data4.txt中</span><br><span class="line">x&#x3D;a([2:2:6],:)&#39;; x&#x3D;nonzeros(x);</span><br><span class="line">t&#x3D;[1790:10:2000]&#39;;</span><br><span class="line">a&#x3D;[ones(21,1), -x(1:end-1)]; </span><br><span class="line">b&#x3D;diff(x).&#x2F;x(1:end-1)&#x2F;10;</span><br><span class="line">cs&#x3D;a\b;</span><br><span class="line">r&#x3D;cs(1), xm&#x3D;r&#x2F;cs(2)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><br>求得：$x_m=294.3860,r=0.0325$</p><p>用以上不同方法得到的人口曲线和原始数据可视化如下图：</p><p><img src="/wiki/%E5%BE%AE%E5%88%86%E6%96%B9%E7%A8%8B%E6%A8%A1%E5%9E%8B-%E4%BA%BA%E5%8F%A3%E6%A8%A1%E5%9E%8B/pic3.jpg" alt="人口预测"></p><blockquote><p>参考：数学建模算法与应用（第2版），司守奎，孙兆亮：第6章 微分方程建模，6.2 人口模型</p><p>MATLAB代码：<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">%Malthus模型%</span><br><span class="line">clc,clear</span><br><span class="line">ezplot(&#39;10*exp(0.1*t)&#39;,[0,100])</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">%Logistic模型%</span><br><span class="line">clc,clear</span><br><span class="line">ezplot(&#39;100&#x2F;(1+((100&#x2F;10)-1)*exp(-0.1*t))&#39;,[0,100])</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">%美国人口预测%</span><br><span class="line">clc,clear</span><br><span class="line">a &#x3D; textread(&#39;data4.txt&#39;);</span><br><span class="line">y &#x3D; a([2:2:6],:)&#39;;</span><br><span class="line">y &#x3D; nonzeros(y);</span><br><span class="line">t &#x3D; [1790:10:2000]&#39;;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">x0 &#x3D; y(1);</span><br><span class="line">t0 &#x3D; t(1);</span><br><span class="line">xm1 &#x3D; 342.4382; xm2 &#x3D; 373.5135; xm3 &#x3D; 294.3860;</span><br><span class="line">r1 &#x3D; 0.0274; r2 &#x3D; 0.0247; r3 &#x3D; 0.0325;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">fplot(@(x) xm1&#x2F;(1+((xm1&#x2F;x0)-1).*exp(-r1.*(x-t0))),[1790,2020],&#39;Linewidth&#39;,2);</span><br><span class="line">hold on</span><br><span class="line">fplot(@(x) xm2&#x2F;(1+((xm2&#x2F;x0)-1).*exp(-r2.*(x-t0))),[1790,2020],&#39;--or&#39;);</span><br><span class="line">fplot(@(x) xm3&#x2F;(1+((xm3&#x2F;x0)-1).*exp(-r3.*(x-t0))),[1790,2020],&#39;-.*c&#39;);</span><br><span class="line">scatter(t,y)</span><br><span class="line">hold off</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">grid on</span><br><span class="line">title(&#39;1790-2020美国人口预测&#39;)</span><br><span class="line">xlabel(&#39;年份&#39;);</span><br><span class="line">ylabel(&#39;人口（百万人）&#39;);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p></blockquote>]]></content>
    
    <summary type="html">
    
      &lt;p&gt;人口模型主要关注人口数量随着时间如何由增长率决定，根据增长率的不同模型可以分为马尔萨斯（Malthus）模型和阻滞增长模型（Logistic 模型），另一个问题是如何利用已有的人口历史数据预测未来的人口，这涉及到参数估计问题。&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
    
    </summary>
    
    
