    <id>http://yoursite.com/wiki/%E7%AC%AC2%E7%AB%A0%E4%B9%A0%E9%A2%98/</id>
    <published>2020-01-24T01:36:30.000Z</published>
    <updated>2020-07-06T02:44:26.574Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<link rel="stylesheet" class="aplayer-secondary-style-marker" href="\assets\css\APlayer.min.css"><script src="\assets\js\APlayer.min.js" class="aplayer-secondary-script-marker"></script><a id="more"></a><p>(1) rand(), inv(), norm(), eye()<br>(2) subs()<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&gt;&gt; syms x s;</span><br><span class="line">&gt;&gt; f&#x3D;x^5+3*x^4+4*x^3+2*x^2+3*x+6;</span><br><span class="line">&gt;&gt; f&#x3D;subs(f,x,(s-1)&#x2F;(s+1))</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><br>(3) simplify()<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&gt;&gt; syms k integer;</span><br><span class="line">&gt;&gt; simplify(sin(k*pi+pi&#x2F;6))</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><br>(4) vpa(), log(), 换底公式<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&gt;&gt; vpa(sqrt(sym(2)),200)</span><br><span class="line">&gt;&gt; vpa((sym(11))^(sym(1&#x2F;6)),200)</span><br><span class="line">&gt;&gt; vpa(sin(sym(pi&#x2F;180)),200)</span><br><span class="line">&gt;&gt; vpa(exp(sym(2)),200)</span><br><span class="line">&gt;&gt; vpa(log(sym(21)),200)</span><br><span class="line">&gt;&gt; vpa(log(exp(sym(1)))&#x2F;log(sym(2)),200)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><br>(5) ①</p><p>(6) assume(), simplify()<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&gt;&gt; exp(sqrt(sym(-1))*sym(pi))+1</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&gt;&gt; syms a;</span><br><span class="line">&gt;&gt; syms k integer;</span><br><span class="line">&gt;&gt; assume(a~&#x3D;pi&#x2F;2+k*pi);</span><br><span class="line">&gt;&gt; simplify((1-2*sin(a)*cos(a))*(1+tan(a))-(cos(a)^2-sin(a)^2)*(1-tan(a)))</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><br>(7) compose(f,g) = f(g(x))<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&gt;&gt; syms x; f&#x3D;x^2-x-1;</span><br><span class="line">&gt;&gt; g&#x3D;f;for i&#x3D;1:10, g&#x3D;compose(f,g),end;</span><br><span class="line">&gt;&gt; simplify(g)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><br>结果太长无法完全显示，暂时没有找到解决方案</p><p>(8) </p>]]></content>
    
